properties.name: Rivers Cocker, Marron and Derwent
properties.river_sea: River Cocker, River Marron, River Derwent
properties.description: Lower Derwent from Bassenthwaite Lake to the coast at Workington. The Cocker from Crummock Water to Cockermouth. The River Marron from Ullock to its confluence with the Derwent near Bridgefoot
